# Fullstack Template Project Structure

This is a monorepo using pnpm workspaces with the following structure:

## Apps Directory

- **Client** (`apps/client/`): React frontend with TanStack Router

  - Main entry: [apps/client/src/main.tsx](mdc:apps/client/src/main.tsx)
  - Routes: [apps/client/src/routes/](mdc:apps/client/src/routes/)
  - UI Components: [apps/client/src/shadcn/components/](mdc:apps/client/src/shadcn/components/)
  - Utilities: [apps/client/src/shadcn/lib/utils.ts](mdc:apps/client/src/shadcn/lib/utils.ts)

- **Server** (`apps/server/`): Express.js backend

  - Main entry: [apps/server/src/index.ts](mdc:apps/server/src/index.ts)
  - Uses the database package as a dependency

- **Database** (`apps/database/`): Drizzle ORM setup
  - Schema: [apps/database/src/schema/](mdc:apps/database/src/schema/)
  - Main export: [apps/database/src/index.ts](mdc:apps/database/src/index.ts)
  - Migrations: [apps/database/drizzle/](mdc:apps/database/drizzle/)

## Key Configuration Files

- Workspace config: [pnpm-workspace.yaml](mdc:pnpm-workspace.yaml)
- Root package: [package.json](mdc:package.json)
- Client config: [apps/client/package.json](mdc:apps/client/package.json)
- Server config: [apps/server/package.json](mdc:apps/server/package.json)
- Database config: [apps/database/package.json](mdc:apps/database/package.json)

## Development Workflow

1. Use `pnpm` as package manager (version 10.1.0)
2. Client runs on Vite dev server
3. Server uses nodemon with tsx for development
4. Database uses Drizzle Kit for migrations

